(317,E'#Footer',E'default',E'<p style="text-align: center;">{{longname}} is the first community of the non-profit organization&nbsp;<a href="https://peercommunityin.org">Peer Community In</a>. The goal of <a href="https://peercommunityin.org">Peer Community In</a> is to promote scientific knowledge. Authors of comments, reviews and recommendations retain copyright© under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/4.0/">CC BY-ND</a>. <a href="../about/contact">Contact &amp; credits</a>. Publication director/directeur de la publication: Denis Bourguet. ISSN: 2551-668X</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; caret-color: #3e3f3a; color: #3e3f3a; text-align: justify;">The PCI project is supported by &nbsp;</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; caret-color: #3e3f3a; color: #3e3f3a; text-align: justify;"><img src="https://peercommunityin.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandeau_sponsors6.png?w=1400" alt="" width="100%"></p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; caret-color: #3e3f3a; color: #3e3f3a; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>'),
